UI DESIGN RULES
[MINDSET] Pick ONE: minimal-editorial | brutalist | retro-future | utilitarian | soft-luxury. Commit fully.
[TYPO]
BANNED: Inter, Roboto, Arial, system-ui. Pick max 2 distinct Google Fonts (e.g., Syne+Lora, SpaceMono+IBM).
Hierarchy: Headings = tracking-tight, leading-[1.2]. Body = leading-relaxed, max-w-[65ch] (mx-auto).
Modifiers: Uppercase MUST use text-xs + tracking-wider. Text-desc MUST reduce opacity/color.
[COLOR & TEXTURE]
BANNED: Tailwind default blue/teal, flat pure #000/#FFF. Use OKLCH or opinionated HEX.
Depth: NO flat solid bg. Use subtle noise (SVG), radial glow, or glassmorphism (bg-black/50 + backdrop-blur-sm).
Shadows: Use color-matched shadows, diffused (e.g., shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgba(X,X,X,0.12)]).
[LAYOUT & MATH STRICTIONS]
8pt Grid: Margin/Padding MUST divide by 4.
Break Symmetry: Asymmetric columns, overlapping, sticky scrolls. Negative space is a tool.
Margin Rule: Outer Margin > 2x Inner Padding.
Radius Math: Child_Radius = Parent_Radius - Padding. Avoid clipping!
[COMPONENTS]
Buttons: Asymmetric (px-4 py-2). MUST have: hover (bg), active (scale-95), disabled (opacity-50), and focus:ring.
Inputs: Visible labels. Focus ring MUST NOT trigger layout shift. Error state = red ring + text-[11px] + icon.
Cards: Combine at least 2 different card treatments per view.
[MOTION & UX]
Intro: Staggered fade-up (delay increments). Hover: 200ms ease-out. Reveals: 600ms. NO bouncing.
Load/Empty: Skeletons (animate-pulse) > Spinners. Empty State BẮT BUỘC có: [Icon mờ + Text + CTA Button].
